**Cooldown Timer**
====================

A simple cooldown timer that can be used to prevent repetitive actions.

### Cooldown Class

```javascript
class Cooldown {
  constructor(duration) {
    this.duration = duration;
    this.lastActivated = null;
  }

  activate() {
    if (this.lastActivated !== null && Date.now() - this.lastActivated < this.duration) {
      return false;
    }
    this.lastActivated = Date.now();
    return true;
  }

  reset() {
    this.lastActivated = null;
  }
}
```

